ip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"73eda22b2d7dfe7884438753aed78fa6233050b6","tid":399583,"uid":54875,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T07:20:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日上完lecture之後同同學飲茶 有男有女咁<br />\n之後就去叫點心<br />\n叫左以下既野食:<br />\n燒賣 x6籠 <br />\n牛肉球 x12籠 個fd on99咁同個點心呀姨調請 叫左勁多 tum個<span style=\"color: red;\">呀姨</span>開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n奶皇鮑 x3籠<br />\n炸兩 x 1籠 <br />\n咸濕角 x 九龍<br />\n<br />\n埋單$95xx<br />\n除返開 每人$57xx <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我見到咁貴 就嬲得濟一野拍落張枱 搞到counter張枱爛左 個呀姨見到我咁大力 就好似鐘意左我 話呢餐唔洗錢 但今晚要我接佢收工 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請問各位巴打我應該要著咩衫去接佢收工好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無圖 你up乜鳩都得㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a1b57fc441bad01ca7981bd2d60945ac345d1d9","tid":399583,"uid":36274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T07:21:28.000Z","msg":"幽默感既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a84f1c1f0d7c002c9358b0dc251152bdba8fbcb5","tid":399583,"uid":72228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T07:22:57.000Z","msg":"聽撚完都打冷震"},{"pid":"ba95514e9f088d2bf30a6784c8a597fb62300036","tid":399583,"uid":128413,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T07:23:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正經答樓主<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/c/c0/Sevenpromop3.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/185?cb=20071010104527\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fc%2Fc0%2FSevenpromop3.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%2Fscale-to-width-down%2F185%3Fcb%3D20071010104527&h=c54af8aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n突顯你返隻無敵金